%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BA%A7n-Qu%C3%A1n/Ho%C3%A1n-kh%C3%AA-sa/poem-yWf4AdRUVLT9FY0uTE02Zw">Hoán khê sa - 浣溪沙</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BA%A7n-Qu%C3%A1n/author-Ahda3BBxTRNmdfIe5Q5e-Q">Tần Quán</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/L%E1%BA%A1c-Du-vi%C3%AAn-ca/poem-YiFCJnfwidfIYZP90LKplQ">Lạc Du viên ca - 樂遊園歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/Thu%E1%BB%B7-thanh/poem-gYNEXcQrM9Fa2ZqBWG9jcA">Thuỷ thanh - 水聲</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%A2n/Tr%C3%BAng-s%E1%BB%91-thi-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-l3xW8fB9YytOsj-6J3Cc7w">Trúng số thi kỳ 1 - 中數詩其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%A2n/author-IGETeQBwf_c0CasyF8dTBQ">Trần Đình Tân</a>)<br></div>	</div>
